 \"Existing high-coverage tests for OkHttp platform internals use local stub classes for optional Android and Jetty ALPN reflective branches; those stubs are useful test code if preserving that coverage, but they are not an external dependency, Docker image, or environment/system property setup.\",\n    \"Native-image verification may still require preserving existing native build configuration such as all-charsets support for `okhttp3.internal.Util`, but this is already part of the existing scaffold rather than new deterministic setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08f43cac743e3695016a3e9c907ccc8197ab3b0a54af395699\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2100, "output": 1092, "cacheRead": 32768, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35960, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782488191241, "responseId": "resp_08f43cac743e3695016a3e9c7fb35c8197a081ceb7a44d26b2"}, "toolResults": []}
